<h3>Publishing Cadence</h3>
<p>Consistency matters more than volume. Publishing 2 to 4 articles per month is realistic for most nonprofit teams. Each article should target a specific keyword, follow <a href="/blog/seo-content-writing/">SEO content writing</a> best practices, and link to relevant internal pages.</p>
<p>Repurpose what you already create. Annual reports become data-driven blog posts. Grant narratives become program explainers. Board presentations become impact articles. You do not need to start from scratch every time.</p>
<h3>Blog Structure for Nonprofits</h3>
